I do not understand the negative reviews; there are much worse superhero films out there; certainly no one could have expected this film to be a historical masterpiece. Here is what You can expect realistically:+ in the comic books, there were 3 Blue Beetles, the film features the third and current one; despite this, it still gives a great hommage to the first and second Beetle characters, especially the second one;
+ while I am not an expert on Blue Beetle, as far as I can tell, the film is authentic, and You can see that the creators wanted to remain true to the character;
+ the casting is successfull, they have found persons who are great fit to their represented roles; (yes, there will be no Oscar-winning performances, but please do not expect that from a superhero film, everyone is still a good fit);
+ the action sequences are good;
+ the jokes are entertaining;
+ there is an emphasis on the family ties; and - not just because of it - but the whole film is a good family movie
+ the music is in line with the plot status; while not always great, sometimes manages to be captivating, I searched for it on Spotify after the movie;
+ yes, there are cliches, but it builds them very cleverly, and it is not that embarrassing at all;
+ yes, there will be a love plot as well, but this is also written carefully; not forced, not rushed, slowly building throughout the film;
+ suprisingly even for me.... I have to say that the film stands up for values. Which is something I did not expected from it. It is a great plus to the creators.Ok, some negatives:
All-in-all, I can recommend to watch this film. Even it is not a masterpiece, I think I will re-view it with friends.

I am not going to write the review about the movie that 278 people have already done it. This review is more about the character of Sister, Milagro Reyes, played by Belissa Escobedo. And what can we learn from this character?Her character puts everyone in danger. Towards the end of the review you shall be able to connect why we need to shut down this type of character right in the beginning.After Jenny hands over the burger box to Jaime she says two things;
a.) Guard this with your life
b.) Do not open this boxJaime heeded the instructions well and gets it to home. He even shares the details with his family so that they are aware and in any case there is an emergency due to that, they are well prepared. But here comes the sister - Milagro who right from the beginning has been shown as a rebellious individual who thinks that she knows the world better than anybody. Trying to be over-smart and brash but zero-contributor in the family. When Jaime clearly said that a. And b. Have to be followed Milagro pushed him to open the box. She also got entire family to push him. The turning point was when she picked up the beetle in her hand and started to tease Jaime while he was trying to put everything in order.Now let's connect the events in the movie because of this one ignorant and immature person;0. Jaime got fired from the job.1. Jaime got transformed in to Beetle with a symbiote in his body. One may say he got super powers but he lost his original form of the body.2. His family house got partially destroyed right in the beginning when he flew out. They had to sell everything just to survive now more damages.3. Victoria Kord and her Team became enemy of the entire family. If the Beetle was not activated or Milagro was not playing with it perhaps the enemy would have been within The Kord Family and not outside in the world.4. His family was captured, the house was burnt down and his father passed away due to heart attack.5. While Jenny and Milagro are running in the tunnels one of the tunnels collapsed and Jenny could have been killed.At no point she realises that all this happened because of her. She was either near or in all the accidents that have happened in the movie including Jaime losing his job.This movie makes us realise that there could be one such person in the family, amongst the friends or work who could possibly put another person in danger. Such character(s) could be skittish at any moment, that is when one has to keep both his/her eyes open and stop the immaturity.I loved the movie, its story, portrayal of the protagonist, visuals and actions...but when I connect the dots I wanted to put Milagro Reyes in jail.
